cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "lean-interest-mgmt: Area-of-interest and zone interest management"
abstract: >
  Lean 4 formal model of area-of-interest (AOI) management and zone interest
  routing for the V-Sekai multiplayer fabric. Specifies cross-zone neighbor
  look-up grounded in lean-spatial-oracle's ZonePartition and interestEntries
  (radius-1 neighborhood covers the full area of interest). Integrates
  lean-rebac-core's NoGod authorization to gate interest delivery by
  relationship policy. Part of the multiplayer-fabric hexagonal architecture.
authors:
